<br>
Takes a long time bet get ac/mana gear. Leave the resists out as you can swap resist gear pretty easy.<br>
<br>
Depending on your lvl will dictate what you can get. Buy always wear gear that gives you good ac and mana. Of course keep wis at 200.<br>
<br>
Hers some kinda easy gear to get as example<br>
<br>
Cone of mystics<br>
Oblus Death shroud<br>
Enshrouded veil<br>
Elec BS ears<br>
<br>
Ur not gonna get big AC / mana at the same time till u get pretty rare stuff. Examples<br>
<br>
SoV druid quest armor<br>
Orb of infinate void<br>
Grotesue belt<br>
<br>
Best of luck<br>
<br>
G<br>
